state.unicode: Action Points||The green bar represents the remaining movement points this force has left. When the green bar is empty, the force will be unable to move until the next turn.
This army is currently without a [[img:icon_general]][[/img]]Lord. A replacement will be appointed during the next turn.

subtemplate.unicode: Set war co-ordination target||Select a mutual enemy settlement or [[img:icon_general]][[/img]]Lord as a target for your allies. This will emphasise the target's strategic importance, so that your allies know to send forces to attack it if they can.
